Hot cocoa, spoilt with blood


Introduction
[Ambiance : ]
This is the story of how I lost myself.
Love was my guide throughout, but I cannot absolve myself of my own responsibility. It would be too easy to put the blame on fate, or on Amélie.
I wish there was a happy ending to this tale.






